`wildcard` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
  $search: {
    "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
    "wildcard": {
      "query": "<search-string>",
      "path": "<field-to-search>",
      "allowAnalyzedField": <boolean>,
      "score": <options>
    }
  }
}
```

